    {
      "content": "## ℹ️  Scan Metrics Not Yet Available\n\nThe four panels above will display data automatically once the **SpiderFoot API** exports a `/metrics` endpoint with the following Prometheus metrics:\n\n| Metric | Type | Description |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| `sf_active_scans` | Gauge | Currently running scans |\n| `sf_scans_started_total` | Counter | Total scans started |\n| `sf_scans_completed_total` | Counter | Total scans completed |\n| `sf_scans_failed_total` | Counter | Total scans failed |\n| `sf_events_produced_total` | Counter | Total OSINT events produced |\n\nAll other panels on this dashboard use **live metrics** from Traefik, Flower, and process exporters.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 10 },
      "id": 15,
      "options": { "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false }, "mode": "markdown" },
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
